subject: The microphone on my laptop is not working
description:
The microphone on my laptop suddenly stopped working already last October. In November Peter took a look and after some extensive testing he fixed the problem. Unfortunately the fix did not last very long and suddenly in December my microphone was again dead. At this stage Peter also looked at the problem remotely and again managed to fix it but again within just a few days the problem was back again. 
This means I have now since months back had to dial in for all of my meetings - which is indeed very cumbersome. Therefore I would hope I can get this fixed asap or a new laptop could be ordered. Even presume my current laptop is still covered by guarantee.
